QuestData.Title: Captain Jack's Dead
QuestData.Description: Gore from Captain Jack's head drips and mysteriously seeps into the ground as you examine your hard-won trophy.$b$bStrange, but no time to investigate that now. There's too much work to be done.$b$bThe chieftain of your newfound friends will doubtlessly be impressed with this proof of your grookin' skills.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring Captain Jack's head to Chief Kah Kah at Grookin Hill.
